\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"rounded-md px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><button type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-slot=\"button\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\" class=\"group/button inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-transparent bg-clip-padding text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/50 active:translate-y-px disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-3 aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:border-destructive/50 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 hover:bg-muted hover:text-foreground aria-expanded:bg-muted aria-expanded:text-foreground dark:hover:bg-muted/50 size-8\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sun size-4 scale-100 rotate-0 transition-all dark:scale-0 dark:-rotate-90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m17.66 17.66 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon absolute size-4 scale-0 rotate-90 transition-all dark:scale-100 dark:rotate-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button></div></div></nav><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col\"><main class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl flex-1 px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"James Nicolaus\",\"jobTitle\":\"Builder & Maintainer, Free Tool Shed\",\"description\":\"James Nicolaus builds and maintains every tool on Free Tool Shed. Each tool is designed, tested in real browsers across desktop and mobile, and shipped only after handling the messy edge cases — large files, slow connections, unusual inputs — that paid alternatives often hide behind sign-up walls.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\",\"worksFor\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Free Tool Shed\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"AboutPage\",\"name\":\"About Free Tool Shed\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\",\"mainEntity\":{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"James Nicolaus\",\"jobTitle\":\"Builder & Maintainer, Free Tool Shed\",\"description\":\"James Nicolaus builds and maintains every tool on Free Tool Shed. Each tool is designed, tested in real browsers across desktop and mobile, and shipped only after handling the messy edge cases — large files, slow connections, unusual inputs — that paid alternatives often hide behind sign-up walls.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\",\"worksFor\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Free Tool Shed\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com\"}}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"About\"}]}</script><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-4\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right size-3.5 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">About</span></li></ol></nav><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">About Free Tool Shed</h1><p class=\"mt-3 text-lg text-muted-foreground\">Free Tool Shed is a growing collection of free, browser-based tools that replace paid software. No sign-up, no downloads, no email harvesting — just open a tool and use it.</p><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch my-8\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Why this site exists</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\">Most everyday digital tasks — generating an invoice, building a resume, merging audio chapters, converting a video, running OCR on a scan — are gated behind subscriptions, mandatory accounts, or seven-day free trials that quietly auto-renew. The tools themselves are not expensive to build. The paywall exists because the alternatives were inconvenient, not because the work behind the tool justified $19, $30, or $49 a month.</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-muted-foreground\">Free Tool Shed exists to make that paywall optional. Every tool on this site does the same job as a paid SaaS equivalent, lives at a permanent URL, and stays free forever. Ads keep the lights on. Your data stays on your device.</p></section><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch my-8\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">How the tools work</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\">Every tool on Free Tool Shed is a standalone web application that runs entirely in your browser. When you create an invoice, build a resume, merge an audiobook, or run OCR on a document, the processing happens on your machine using modern web technologies — WebAssembly for the heavy tools (ffmpeg.wasm, Tesseract.js), the Web Audio API, the Canvas API, and the browser&#x27;s built-in PDF and media stack.</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-muted-foreground\">Nothing is uploaded. There are no servers that hold your files. Your work auto-saves to your browser&#x27;s local storage so you can come back later, and when you export, the finished file goes straight to your device&#x27;s download folder.</p><div class=\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl flex gap-3 p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-dollar-sign mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"2\" y2=\"22\"></line><path d=\"M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Free, forever</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">No subscriptions, no freemium tiers, no &quot;free trial&quot; that expires. Ad-supported so the tools stay free for everyone.</p></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl flex gap-3 p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Private by design</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Everything runs in your browser. Your files, data, and documents never leave your device — we can&#x27;t see them, and neither can anyone else.</p></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl flex gap-3 p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">No sign-up</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">No account creation, no email verification, no onboarding flow. Open the tool and start using it.</p></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl flex gap-3 p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-code-xml mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m18 16 4-4-4-4\"></path><path d=\"m6 8-4 4 4 4\"></path><path d=\"m14.5 4-5 16\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Built to last</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Each tool lives at a permanent URL. No deprecation cycles, no pivots to a different product. If a tool ships, it stays.</p></div></div></div></section><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch my-8\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">How tools are chosen</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\">Tools are added based on a simple test: is there a common task gated behind a paid SaaS that a modern browser can do natively? If the answer is yes, it&#x27;s a candidate. Priority goes to tools where the paid alternative is either expensive, requires a sign-up just to generate a single file, or asks for sensitive data (financial, personal, professional) that shouldn&#x27;t leave a user&#x27;s device.</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-muted-foreground\">Every tool is built to handle the messy edge cases — large files, multi-page documents, unusual input formats, slow connections — that paid alternatives often hide behind their sign-up wall. If a tool can&#x27;t handle a real-world workload, it doesn&#x27;t ship.</p></section><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch my-8\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">About the maintainer</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\">Free Tool Shed is built and maintained by<!-- --> <span class=\"font-medium text-foreground\">James Nicolaus</span>. Every tool is designed, implemented, and tested in real browsers before it ships. The same person who writes the code answers the contact email, fixes the bugs, and decides what gets built next.</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-muted-foreground\">If you find a bug, want a tool that doesn&#x27;t exist yet, or want to flag something that should be improved, the contact form is the fastest way to reach the maintainer directly.</p></section><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch my-8\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Editorial standards</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\">Comparison tables on tool pages are based on the publicly listed features and pricing of the alternatives at the time of publication. If a paid alternative changes its pricing or adds a free tier, the comparison gets updated. Tool pages disclose every limitation honestly — if a Free Tool Shed tool doesn&#x27;t support a feature the paid alternative does, the comparison says so.</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-muted-foreground\">Free Tool Shed does not accept paid placement, sponsored reviews, or affiliate kickbacks from the SaaS alternatives it compares against. The ads you see on the site are run through standard ad networks and are not endorsements.</p></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div><footer class=\"border-t border-border bg-muted/40\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-4 px-4 py-8 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Free Tool Shed. All rights reserved.</p><nav class=\"flex gap-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/terms\">Terms</a></nav></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0eyplc079uusk.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[83661,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\\\"],\\\"ThemeProvider\\\"]\\n3:I[46798,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\\\",\\\"/_n