ull,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-medium text-foreground\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"James Nicolaus\\\"}],\\\". Every tool is designed, implemented, and tested in real browsers before it ships. The same person who writes the code answers the contact email, fixes the bugs, and decides what gets built next.\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-3 text-muted-foreground\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"If you find a bug, want a tool that doesn't exist yet, or want to flag something that should be improved, the contact form is the fastest way to reach the maintainer directly.\\\"}]]}]\\n1c:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L15\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"my-8\\\"}]\\n1d:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Editorial standards\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Comparison tables on tool pages are based on the publicly listed features and pricing of the alternatives at the time of publication. If a paid alternative changes its pricing or adds a free tier, the comparison gets updated. Tool pages disclose every limitation honestly — if a Free Tool Shed tool doesn't support a feature the paid alternative does, the comparison says so.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-3 text-muted-foreground\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Free Tool Shed does not accept paid placement, sponsored reviews, or affiliate kickbacks from the SaaS alternatives it compares against. The ads you see on the site are run through standard ad networks and are not endorsements.\\\"}]]}]\\n1e:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",\\\"script-0\\\",{\\\"src\\\":\\\"/_next/static/chunks/064cw2la3d-ye.js\\\",\\\"async\\\":true,\\\"nonce\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\"}]\\n1f:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L28\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$24\\\",null,{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Next.MetadataOutlet\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"$@29\\\"}]}]\\n\"