Your files, data, and documents never leave your device — we can't see them, and neither can anyone else.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"data-slot\":\"card\",\"data-size\":\"default\",\"className\":\"group/card flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[>img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl flex gap-3 p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\",\"key\":\"1xq2db\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-zap mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],\"$L26\"]}],\"$L27\"]}]]}]\n18:[\"$\",\"$L15\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8\"}]\n19:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"How tools are chosen\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Tools are added based on a simple test: is there a common task gated behind a paid SaaS that a modern browser can do natively? If the answer is yes, it's a candidate. Priority goes to tools where the paid alternative is either expensive, requires a sign-up just to generate a single file, or asks for sensitive data (financial, personal, professional) that shouldn't leave a user's device.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Every tool is built to handle the messy edge cases — large files, multi-page documents, unusual input formats, slow connections — that paid alternatives often hide behind their sign-up wall. If a tool can't handle a real-world workload, it doesn't ship.\"}]]}]\n1a:[\"$\",\"$L15\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8\"}]\n1b:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"About the maintainer\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[\"Free Tool Shed is built and maintained by\",\" \",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium text-foreground\",\"children\":\"James Nicolaus\"}],\". Every tool is designed, implemented, and tested in real browsers before it ships. The same person who writes the code answers the contact email, fixes the bugs, and decides what gets built next.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"If you find a bug, want a tool that doesn't exist yet, or want to flag something that should be improved, the contact form is the fastest way to reach the maintainer directly.\"}]]}]\n1c:[\"$\",\"$L15\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8\"}]\n1d:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Editorial standards\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Comparison tables on tool pages are based on the publicly listed features and pricing of the alternatives at the time of publication. If a paid alternative changes its pricing or adds a free tier, the comparison gets updated. Tool pages disclose every limitation honestly — if a Free Tool Shed tool doesn't support a feature the paid alternative does, the comparison says so.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Free Tool Shed does not accept paid placement, sponsored reviews, or affiliate kickbacks from the SaaS alternatives it compares against. The ads you see on the site are run through standard ad networks and are not endorsements.\"}]]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"script\",\"script-0\",{\"src\":\"/_next/static/chunks/064cw2la3d-ye.js\",\"async\":true,\"nonce\":\"$undefined\"}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"$L28\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$24\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@29\"}]}]\n26:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"No sign-up\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"No account creation, no email verification, no onboarding flow. Open the tool and start using it.\"}]]}]\n27:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"data-slot\":\"card\",\"data-size\":\"default\",\"className\":\"group/card flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[>img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl flex gap-3 p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m18 16 4-4-4-4\",\"key\":\"1inbqp\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m6 8-4 4 4 4\",\"key\":\"15zrgr\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m14.5 4-5 16\",\"key\":\"e7oirm\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-code-xml mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Built to last\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Each tool lives at a permanent URL. No deprecation cycles, no pivots to a different product. If a tool ships, it stays.\"}]]}]]}]\n22:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\n2a:I[27201,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\"],\"IconMark\"]\n25:[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"About |